OL,3,CFormer miners to finally receive money
OL,4,Ckept from pensions for decades
OL,6,FThe government has announced moves to
OL,7,Foverturn an "historic injustice"
OL,8,Finvolving former mineworkers who have
OL,9,Fhad money withheld from their pensions
OL,10,Fsince 1994.
OL,12,FFollowing the news in Wednesday's
OL,13,FBudget, Energy Secretary Ed Miliband
OL,14,Fsaid more than 100,000 former
OL,15,Fmineworkers will receive #1.5 billion
OL,16,Fof money kept from their pensions.
