OL,3,CFormer miners to finally receive money
OL,4,Ckept from pensions for decades
OL,6,FHe confirmed the move will mean a 32%
OL,7,Fincrease to the annual pensions of
OL,8,F112,000 former mineworkers, an average
OL,9,Fincrease of #29 per week for each
OL,10,Fmember.
OL,12,FWhen the Mineworkers' Pension Scheme
OL,13,Fwas privatised in 1994, it was agreed
OL,14,Fthat 50 per cent of all surplus money
OL,15,Fgenerated by the scheme would be paid
OL,16,Fdirectly to the state, as buffer
OL,17,Fagainst any future deficit.
