OL,3,CFormer miners to finally receive money
OL,4,Ckept from pensions for decades
OL,6,FHowever, it left many members
OL,7,Fsignificantly worse off, with the
OL,8,Faverage former miner getting a pension
OL,9,Fof just #84 a week ` and widows even
OL,10,Fless.
OL,12,FThe surplus fund, now worth #1.5
OL,13,Fbillion, will be handed back to the
OL,14,Fpension scheme.
OL,16,FMiliband said: "We owe the mining
OL,17,Fcommunities who powered this country a
OL,18,Fdebt of gratitude.
