OL,3,CFormer miners to finally receive money
OL,4,Ckept from pensions for decades
OL,6,F"For decades, it has been a scandal
OL,7,Fthat the government has taken money
OL,8,Fthat could have been passed to the
OL,9,Fminers and their families.
OL,11,F"Today, that scandal ends, and the
OL,12,Fmoney is rightfully transferred to the
OL,13,Fminers. I pay tribute to the
OL,14,Fcampaigners who have fought for
OL,15,Fjustice, today is their victory."
