OL,3,CFormer miners to finally receive money
OL,4,Ckept from pensions for decades
OL,6,FMinister for Industry Sarah Jones
OL,7,Fsaid: "Miners powered our industries
OL,8,Fand our homes for decades. That's why
OL,9,Fwe have to right the wrong that has
OL,10,Fdenied them the decent pension they
OL,11,Fdeserved.
OL,13,F"We are handing over the #1.5 billion
OL,14,Fthat for years has sat in the reserve
OL,15,Ffund unused at times when people
OL,16,Fneeded it most.
