OL,3,CFormer miners to finally receive money
OL,4,Ckept from pensions for decades
OL,6,F"This will end an historic injustice
OL,7,Fand will ensure members of the scheme
OL,8,Fsee an average increase of #29 per
OL,9,Fweek added to their pay, an increase
OL,10,Fof 32%."
OL,12,FGary Saunders, chairman of the
OL,13,FTrustees of the Mineworkers' Pension
OL,14,FScheme, said: "As a Trustee board we
OL,15,Fare delighted we will be able to put
OL,16,Fmore money in our members' pockets.
OL,18,F"We are also grateful to the many
OL,19,Fmembers and MPs who have shown support
OL,20,Fof the scheme on this matter over the
OL,21,Fyears."
